{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01QuxU5PZgxWWLauwWYt6JJa","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I can see both issues:\n\n1. **Configure permission is empty** (`\"configure\":\"\"`): `app-user` can't declare/create queues.\n2. **`force-quorum` policy** on `/app` vhost forces all queues to quorum type, conflicting with the producer's `x-queue-type: classic` request.\n\nI'll fix both by running a one-shot pod that calls the management API:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1633,"cache_read_input_tokens":35385,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1633},"output_tokens":24,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0a1f5e8a-4307-43cd-a3d6-52110567492e","uuid":"e325963a-3060-4824-bc15-3186dfa81346","request_id":"req_011CbyECntnY1wU7NSJhizH8"}
